   Captify recrute un Sales Manager – H/F

   Partager la publication "Captify recrute un Sales Manager – H/F"

   captify-logo_200x200
   9 Rue Ampère, 75017 Paris
   www.captify.fr

   Partager la publication "Captify recrute un Sales Manager – H/F"

   Are you a passionate Sales professional? Do you want to be a part of
   something great? Captify are looking for a Sales Manager to join our
   successful team in Paris. You will be leading relationships with key FR
   agencies and driving performance.

Benefits

     * Competitive base salary and commission structure
     * Central Paris location
     * Be a part of something great, join at a time of rapid growth
     * Free food and drink
     * Healthcare including yoga

Key responsibilities

     * Presenting Captify’s proposition to clients and agencies
     * Responding to agency briefs and proactive communicating ideas to
       clients on how they can use Captify
     * Responsible for up-selling and working with the existing sales team
       to increase revenue from a particular patch
     * Grow revenue and increase retention of clients/agencies.
     * Encourage feedback from customers to enhance products and services.

Your background

     * Comfortable working in a sales environment with individual and team
       targets
     * Target driven
     * Proactive approach with excellent communication skills via email,
       over the phone and in person.
     * Passion for digital and always seeking to extend your knowledge of
       the market.

How to apply

   To apply please contact Captify at jobs@captify.fr or visit its
   website here

