   Captify recrute un Senior Sales Manager – H/F

   Partager la publication "Captify recrute un Senior Sales Manager – H/F"

   captify-logo_200x200
   9 Rue Ampère, 75017 Paris
   www.captify.fr

   Partager la publication "Captify recrute un Senior Sales Manager – H/F"

   Are you a driven and experienced Sales professional? Do you want to
   work for a company where you can be part of something great? Captify
   are looking for a Senior Sales Manager who will be responsible for
   selling Captify’s Search Intelligence products to advertising buyers in
   the France. You must have extensive media buyer/planner contacts at key
   FR agencies, and must be able to demonstrate a proven sales history.

Benefits

     * Competitive base salary and commission structure
     * Central Paris location
     * Be a part of something great, join at a time of rapid growth
     * Free food and drink
     * Healthcare including yoga

Key responsibilities

     * Selling Captify’s Search Intelligence DR, Brand and video
       advertising products
     * Sourcing, pitching and closing agency deals.
     * Helping to build sales strategy for a given agency group
     * Identifying commercial opportunities within an agency group and
       working with the senior management team to bring those to market
     * Helping to open doors and leverage existing relationship to help
       the wider team
     * Maintaining senior level relationships at agency group level
     * Be a driving force within the senior sales team to deliver
       best-practise across the market
     * Have an excellent knowledge of the DR, brand and video markets to
       help deliver revenue growth across those channels

Requirements

     * Strong track record of performance against targets
     * Demonstrated passion for data and technology and its use in driving
       revenue and customer satisfaction
     * Exceptional written/verbal communication and presentation skills
       across all customer levels, partners, and stakeholders
     * Strong track record of performance against targets
     * Demonstrated passion for data and technology and its use in driving
       revenue and customer satisfaction
     * Exceptional written/verbal communication and presentation skills
       across all customer levels, partners, and stakeholders

How to apply

   To apply please contact Captify at jobs@captify.fr or visit its
   website here

