   12 février 2019
   Captify recrute un Programmatic Trader – H/F

   Partager la publication "Captify recrute un Programmatic Trader – H/F"

   captify-logo_200x200
   9 Rue Ampère, 75017 Paris
   www.captify.fr

   Partager la publication "Captify recrute un Programmatic Trader – H/F"

   Are you passionate about providing an excellent service? Do you pride
   yourself in the high quality work that you produce? Captify are looking
   to add an Account Manager to our fast growing team based in Paris.

What you will be doing…

     * Day to day management of accounts, including weekly reporting and
       pacing checks
     * Best in class service levels
     * Campaign set up
     * Primary point of contact for client via email/phone
     * Answer client queries via email
     * Liaising with TAMs, Sales, CS and Trading teams
     * Create basic PCAs including campaign specific reports
     * Performance tracking
     * Reconciliations
     * Make upweight recommendations to CS team

 What you will need to have…

     * Account management or customer service experience
     * Proficient use of Microsoft Excel
     * Excellent attention to details
     * Good prioritization and time management skills
     * Excellent communicator with both internal and external stakeholders
     * Able to multitask and, at times, manage a large workload

 What’s in it for you…

     * Competitive base salary
     * Paris 17 – Wagram – Rue Ampère
     * 25 days holiday – plus bank holidays, your birthday and a volunteer
       day
     * You are not just a number at Captify, your work makes a difference
     * A range of flexible benefits

How to apply

   To apply please contact Captify at jobs@captify.fr or visit its
   website here

